{"tid":1624204,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"天琦上訴眾籌 推啊","createTime":"2019-10-05T03:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T05:31:38.000Z","uid":245127,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"38b40765375de7e590d5698e52d6d8dbe4feecfe","tid":1624204,"uid":245127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:12:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">立即入去捐錢同幫推！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/edwardleungappeal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fedwardleungappeal%2F&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqnKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=4342a281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/edwardleungappeal/</a></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<em>利申：同義工隊冇關係</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">【為天琦刑期上訴眾籌】<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n各位愛護天琦的香港人：<br />\n<br />\n相信大家一直有關注天琦的消息，他的刑期上訴聆訊將於<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">10月9日在高等法院審理</span></span>。天琦的家人及好友慎重權衡後，決定聘請資深大律師代表天琦上訴。由於所費不菲，我們無奈之下發起眾籌，冀望聚沙成塔，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標金額為35萬，誠盼各位可與天琦同行。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n義工小組 敬上<br />\n<br />\n眾籌連結：<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/edwardleungappeal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fedwardleungappeal%2F&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqnKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=4342a281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/edwardleungappeal/</a><br />\n眾籌目標：35萬港元（包括平台手續費6.9%，達標即止，為免加重大家的負擔，我們希望每人捐款不多於1000元）<br />\n<br />\n【Call for funding for Edward Leung's sentence appeal】<br />\n<br />\nDear fellow Hong Kongers,<br />\n<br />\nAs you all know, Edward&rsquo;s sentence appeal hearing will be held in the High Court on October 9.  After much thought and consideration, we decided to hire a senior counsel to represent Edward in the appeal case.  In order to cover the significant legal costs, we would like to raise HK$350,000 through crowdfunding.  We sincerely hope that you could give Edward a hand and thank you in advance for your contribution.<br />\n<br />\nWith warmest regards,<br />\nEdward&rsquo;s Volunteer Team<br />\n<br />\nCrowdfunding link: <a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/edwardleungappeal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fedwardleungappeal%2F&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqnKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=4342a281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/edwardleungappeal/</a><br />\nCrowdfunding target: HK$350,000 &ndash; including the platform handling fee of 6.9% and will end once the target is met. We advise that each person shall donate no more than HK$1,000."},{"pid":"9de61ca38aa51b6ad23cfcb8a5324033ef174353","tid":1624204,"uid":245127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:14:25.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"c70d68c0cab033e702b0a391120f45aec02f39c0","tid":1624204,"uid":245127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:14:38.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"9bfef40499240182bbb21d93793917129654927b","tid":1624204,"uid":245127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:14:48.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"172ac2f9691e701f52e1c3ec5f8a73f45616d0ad","tid":1624204,"uid":245127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:14:58.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"b0138f4a580e7e0a2775b8da2ed0a5f64273a501","tid":1624204,"uid":245127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:15:08.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"0fb46fd521ec05d512fe7261d55cc9573e73fd6